@PurpleRooster  
Yes, but you can copy it with [reverberate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=reverberate) or [chandra, the firebrand](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=chandra, the firebrand), then if the copy hits another reverberate you can use that to copy the original again...  
You'd need quite a bit of luck (and mana) to pull that off, but it could be fairly spectacular.
